  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >simple 2D platformer with just jumps and hooks!</h2><br><strong>Features of this game</strong><br>1. Minimalist Visuals and story<br>2. Extremely Simplified Controls<br>3. Abundant gimmicks and a variety of level designs<br>4. Challenging difficulty and rewarding achievements<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/8962f84d24902b82fe698124f54090b2.poster.avif?t=1691500632\" width=434 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/8962f84d24902b82fe698124f54090b2.webm?t=1691500632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/8962f84d24902b82fe698124f54090b2.mp4?t=1691500632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Only device used is mouse. Jump with left-click!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/5958dca87b1bb84f638bd700a49c220a.poster.avif?t=1691500632\" width=438 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/5958dca87b1bb84f638bd700a49c220a.webm?t=1691500632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/5958dca87b1bb84f638bd700a49c220a.mp4?t=1691500632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Hook with right-click. It delivers you more (cannot use at first)!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/4a348ec989738219f6d21fe9a686a614.poster.avif?t=1691500632\" width=438 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/4a348ec989738219f6d21fe9a686a614.webm?t=1691500632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/4a348ec989738219f6d21fe9a686a614.mp4?t=1691500632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If any mistakes, you can restart right away!<br><br><br>Feel free to webcast, video production or monetize (including super chat).<br>I hope you enjoy it!<br><br>amay.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >simple 2D platformer with just jumps and hooks!</h2><br><strong>Features of this game</strong><br>1. Minimalist Visuals and story<br>2. Extremely Simplified Controls<br>3. Abundant gimmicks and a variety of level designs<br>4. Challenging difficulty and rewarding achievements<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/8962f84d24902b82fe698124f54090b2.poster.avif?t=1691500632\" width=434 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/8962f84d24902b82fe698124f54090b2.webm?t=1691500632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/8962f84d24902b82fe698124f54090b2.mp4?t=1691500632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Only device used is mouse. Jump with left-click!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/5958dca87b1bb84f638bd700a49c220a.poster.avif?t=1691500632\" width=438 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/5958dca87b1bb84f638bd700a49c220a.webm?t=1691500632\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/5958dca87b1bb84f638bd700a49c220a.mp4?t=1691500632\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Hook with right-click. It delivers you more (cannot use at first)!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463930/extras/4a348ec989738219f6d21fe9a686a614.poster.avif?t=1691500632\" width=438 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.